{"tid":1204710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致香港警察，請你撫摸自己良心","createTime":"2019-06-11T15:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T15:49:52.000Z","uid":4563,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9185145a1477721eb651700f29c928bd85692e09","tid":1204710,"uid":4563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:54:38.000Z","msg":"得大陸版出得咁快<br />\n對唔住，殘體字黎既<br />\n<br />\n請你地好好諗下自己做差人係為咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左扑濕市民？<br />\n為左成為政府既棋子？<br />\n面對不公義不公平都繼續漠視，甚至乎做幫兇？<br />\n淨係識收order做事？唔經大腦思考？<br />\n定你為左份糧，甘願埋沒良心？<br />\n<br />\n德國既防暴警察都曾經試過倒戈幫市民<br />\n香港皇家警察點解你地做唔到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔要求你地辭職，但希望你地行動之前，試下思考並反駁下上司<br />\n<br />\n你地係人，唔係狗<br />\n唔啱既野應該要好似市民咁站出黎反抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7kqcEZv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7kqcEZv.png&h=8c0b95f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EaRLfxR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEaRLfxR.png&h=b2cf887b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/41NiAxS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F41NiAxS.png&h=53d776e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJk8djz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJk8djz.png&h=8bacbfb8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a871c460550e75a883b1115700f0bd7dfdbd8bff","tid":1204710,"uid":139916,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:55:57.000Z","msg":"佢地唔識保住個良心，只識保住個後面"},{"pid":"abf3f6ca995e57da043097f4344caa720b9cab60","tid":1204710,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T15:56:04.000Z","msg":"其實VIU OTT有 唔洗上Youku<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.viu.com/ott/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.viu.com%2Fott%2Fhk%2F